{"tid":1244221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"衝定唔衝唔應該係預先set死 但要準備","createTime":"2019-06-19T21:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T05:38:27.000Z","uid":129592,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"98d2f82cd73d6380c93200938cca2fb451637e3f","tid":1244221,"uid":129592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T21:34:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係呀發夢呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多post已經研究緊衝定唔衝，但現場衝定唔衝，好睇前線人手數量，<span style=\"color: red;\">講緊係前線會分工衝而唔係齋企嘅人。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">621究竟有幾多人冇人會知，如果前線人員唔夠，寧願坐都咪亂衝搏清場搏受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記得切勿戀戰！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">衝嘅，自己睇返出面巴打整合嘅裝備清單。裝備個身，唔該都裝備個心。個個都驚中彈，但係唔係一聽到聲就拉隊退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係頂唔順嘅，麻煩都拉返人返嚟，頭兩排打緊近身戰，根本唔會知後面退咗。<span style=\"color: red;\">前面巴打食棍又食椒，中後要走都拉返佢地，唔好由佢地死呀！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外，如果可以，每個人都大概睇下可以點滅催淚彈。冇人可以預計到時粒嘢飛去邊，所以大家都要有基本知識！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位，621發夢見。</span>"},{"pid":"173cce37744f5258a466c4e1645ab22d9f69e531","tid":1244221,"uid":129592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:38:27.000Z","msg":"雖然已經好多po，不過都自推下！<br />\n加油呀咁多位手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}